          <a href="https://roykung.tumblr.com/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Tumblr</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          I share my slides on{' '}
          <a href="https://www.slideshare.net/roykung" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Slideshare</a> and{' '}
          <a href="https://speakerdeck.com/roykung" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">SpeakDeck</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can find me on <a href="https://twitter.com/roylinkung" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Twitter</a>,
          or drop me an Email.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
      <div class="mx-auto w-3/4">
        <img src="/profile.jpeg" alt="Roy Lin 林昆彥" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 
